These are scripts and configuration files for the remote PC
system based on Tiny Core Linux 14.0. Key shell scripts are:

opt/bootlocal.sh - Set-up commands run at the end of the boot
                   process. (run as root)

usr/local/bin/menu.sh - The menu displayed to the user for
                        connecting to a network using either WiFi or
                        Ethernet, or changing the audio volume.
                        (run as root)
